TY  - JOUR
TI  - On the Welfare Analysis of Rational Expectations Equilibria with Asymmetric Information
AU  - Laffont, Jean-Jacques
AB  - [Rational expectations equilibria are analyzed as incentive compatible mechanisms. The sense in which they can be implemented is made precise. Then, a welfare analysis of these equilibria is carried out within the class of mechanisms having the same incentive compatibility properties and the same communication constraints.]
C1  - Full publication date: Jan., 1985
DB  - JSTOR
DO  - 10.2307/1911721
EP  - 29
IS  - 1
PB  - [Wiley, Econometric Society]
PY  - 1985
